'''Taqa''' d yiwet taddart n [[Tamurt Taqbaylit|tmurt taqbaylit]] tɣiwant n [[At Yeḥya]], deg tdayra n [[Tadayra n Uṣqif n Ṭmana|Uṣqif n Ṭmana]] di [[Tawilayt n Tizi Uzzu|twilayt n Tizi Wezzu]]. 

== Tarakalt ==

=== Asideg ===

Taddart tezga-d ar 10 km seg [[Aṣqif n Ṭmana]] ed 50 km seg [[Tizi Wezzu]]. 

=== Igemmamen ed tixljetin n Taqa ===

Zikenni, Taqa n At Yeḥya am akkw tuddar n Yiqbayliyen ɣur-es imir-a 7 n txelajatin : 

[[Tafrawt]] – [[Iṣendlen]] – [[Agni n Yesɛed]] - [[Lemxarda]]  - [[At Si Ɛmara]] - [[At Buteččur]] ed [[At Ḥmed]], tixeljatin-a llan d aḥric n Taqa n sebɛa iwegiden. 

== Iderman n Taqa ==
 
Llan kkuẓ (4) iderman di Taqa  :

- '''At Mlula''' ay d adrum meqquren akk wiyaḍ di Taqa, ad naf gar-asen tiwaculin tigini : At Wares, Maḥyu, At Ḥemmu, Lefki, Ben Ccix, At Sɛada, At Qasi, Lqaḍi, At Seɛdi…

- '''Iɛezuzen''' : wis sin akwd At Hebuc, Iɛezuzen, At Ɛmer, Sayad , Mesɛudi, Ɛezzi,  At Ḥemmu ed Bennur.

- '''Lemxarda''' : akwd twaculin n At Ɛli, At Qasi Weɛli, Ḥamudi, At Ḥemmu Weɛli, At Ɛli u Yeḥya

- '''At Leḥsen''' : At Ḥammaduc, At Ɛemara, At Saɛid, Aoudjehane, At Yeḥya.

=== Taliwin n Taqa ===

Llant azal n 13 taliwin deg Taqa n At Yeḥya : Tala n Weẓru, Meqqucca, Agwni Hegini, Akhemchane, Tala n Yilef, Tala n Tirḍa, Lɛinṣer, Budmuyen, Ɛebbas, Tala Ybuba, Amcerir, Afarzal, Tala Lemxarda.



